當新註冊死架?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打點睇現時畫畫既狀況<br />\n其實我見好多人都開始畫插畫 IG更多</blockquote><br />\n其實我淨係見到一堆人係到放閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />作為一條撚樣，自然無興趣睇人幾幸福<br />\n<br />\n我想睇到既係人地用心血畫，有愛既作品<br />\n唔一定要搞笑諷刺又唔一定要色情灰暗<br />\n唔一定係漫畫唔一定係插畫<br />\n<br />\n我唔信香港淨係會出到一個門小雷"},{"pid":"c803d0077f3dd8f553052316bcfd09e5b708d329","tid":412271,"uid":56498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"其實仲有班人畫紋身畫漫畫搞平面好正<br />\n<br />\n鬼仔叫art、painting，good、awesome <br />\n香港叫畫公仔，廢柴，興趣搵唔到食<br />\n<br />\n明啦屌，唔洗多講"},{"pid":"10171a0247c7d79e49219d7b53afcbebebbd8d7c","tid":412271,"uid":138667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"門小雷真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa0b7cd10462f7330c444a6ad46cf798439e05a","tid":412271,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>門小雷真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最近啲幾格漫畫好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b77b35672d709e73d0890e37845983103eaebf","tid":412271,"uid":141462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得香港叫出名又幾靚既有謝晒皮 kazy 含蓄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有無其他介紹</blockquote><br />\nkazy水彩幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nKazy<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab1988171534f389da7eb5a040e6df2f84cc92b","tid":412271,"uid":72613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>門小雷真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真係好撚正 數漏咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56a92aa923010fb79cc9229b296e1693c07f258","tid":412271,"uid":72613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>門小雷真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最近啲幾格漫畫好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢錄左畫線條個啲筆順 順到喊<br />\n真係台下十年功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3533ea31302a44f5a0181a249fd651525c0dcba","tid":412271,"uid":72613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:34:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實仲有班人畫紋身畫漫畫搞平面好正<br />\n<br />\n鬼仔叫art、painting，good、awesome <br />\n香港叫畫公仔，廢柴，興趣搵唔到食<br />\n<br />\n明啦屌，唔洗多講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢啲想睇啲有心畫畫既人已經少之有少<br />\n我見有啲畫到好靚既偏偏無人欣賞<br />\n小畫家幾條線既就幾千讚 咩眼光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9bd335af5c17d2c645aec00b54ede7259e79d1","tid":412271,"uid":72613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實仲有班人畫紋身畫漫畫搞平面好正<br />\n<br />\n鬼仔叫art、painting，good、awesome <br />\n香港叫畫公仔，廢柴，興趣搵唔到食<br />\n<br />\n明啦屌，唔洗多講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢<del>啲</del> <strong>家</strong> 想睇啲有心畫畫既人已經少之有少<br />\n我見有啲畫到好靚既偏偏無人欣賞<br />\n小畫家幾條線既就幾千讚 咩眼光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"29b337485af14a9e963e64b0621364ee08f1f7a0","tid":412271,"uid":72613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:36:54.000Z","msg":"我的港女老婆個咳神畫功都好靚其實<br />\n見到佢啲手繪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}